@host = http://localhost:5048
### JWT HS256: iss=OrderService aud=OrderService, key = appsettings Jwt:SigningKey; claims: sub, name, exp (future).
@token = PASTE_JWT_HERE

### Danh sách đơn (phân trang, lọc name — map vào Code lưu trữ)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/orders?name=&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Tạo đơn (body khớp docs/openapi.yml)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
IdempotentId: 

{
  "date": "2026-03-29",
  "totalAmount": 1000000,
  "totalDiscountAmount": 50000,
  "totalPaymentAmount": 950000,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "prd_001",
      "productName": "Dịch vụ A",
      "unitPrice": 500000,
      "quantity": 2,
      "amount": 1000000,
      "discountAmount": 50000,
      "paymentAmount": 950000
    }
  ]
}

###

### Checkout (thay {orderId} bằng id trả về khi tạo đơn)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentServiceId": "pay_svc_live_01",
  "paymentMethod": "card"
}

###
